OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FVariable
OL,6,Fcloud and some sunny then clear spells
OL,7,Ffor the Hebrides. Otherwise, cloudy
OL,8,Fwith outbreaks of rain, these heavy
OL,9,Fand thundery at times in the evening.
OL,10,FRain largely clearing east by morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAny overnight rain soon
OL,13,Fclearing east. Otherwise cooler and
OL,14,Fmainly cloudy with some patchy light
OL,15,Fdrizzle possible, but west coast
OL,16,Fbrightening up with some warm sunshine
OL,17,Fbreaking out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
