OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with some sunshine at times,
OL,7,Fespecially Monday. Very warm in the
OL,8,Fwest with the best of the sunshine,
OL,9,Fcloudier at times in the east.
